!!~FreeDV settings when using QMX:


<<<
There's an option in Tools->Options->Rig Control called ''"Use USB/LSB instead of DIGU/DIGL"''; this will need to be enabled for FreeDV to work with the QMX (otherwise, FreeDV will switch the radio into DIGU or DIGL modes, which are what you'd use for single carrier modes like FT8).
