!!~FreeDV does not display waterfall until you disable AGC


<<<
I've noticed with mine that the waterfall in FreeDV is basically black unless there's a signal coming in. This appears to be due to how the AGC works on the QMX by default. Setting "AGC Threshold S" to 0 (more info: https://groups.io/g/QRPLabs/message/158563) at least causes FreeDV to show noise on the waterfall and increases the audio volume a bit.
